Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:11.74,*Default,Yumi,0,0,0,,体检完的女生  请排队进行下一项检查!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:13.92,*Default,Elis,0,0,0,,这些是测量胸围的卷尺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:15.71,*Default,Elis,0,0,0,,你们可以互相测量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.03,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,拉娜同学 81公分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.80,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,好了 我们交换
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:23.00,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,根本就不需要用卷尺~的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.64,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,圣门八极拳的基础!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.22,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,通过感知来测量!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.14,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,那是哪招啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:31.18,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,柊同学 77公分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:33.35,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,等等 这只有这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:37.52,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,我还希望能大一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:39.18,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,会慢慢成长的啦~的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:41.72,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,因为你还处在成长期嘛~的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:43.85,*Default,Ganessa,0,0,0,,啊啦 那正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:47.85,*Default,Ganessa,0,0,0,,那位同学 也来帮我量看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:51.22,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,那确实值得测量~的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:52.64,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,真…真大!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:55.14,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:57.77,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,嘉涅莎同学 83公分~的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:00:59.97,*Default,Ganessa,0,0,0,,哦呵呵呵~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.18,*Default,Ganessa,0,0,0,,或许有点发育过头了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:07.02,*Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,什…什么嘛 那种贬低人的眼神!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.27,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,萨提莱莎·艾尔·布列吉特同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.81,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,竟然有90公分!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:14.22,*Default,Satella,0,0,0,,所以我才讨厌体检…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:17.77,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,你凭什么讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.02,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,我才是最讨厌体检的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:24.81,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,学生会长 西凤·菲尔查德 82公分!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:29.72,*Default,Rana,0,0,0,,副会长 提茜·菲尼尔 83公分!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:34.02,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,看来我装傻也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:37.68,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,亚提亚同学 你在这里做什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:40.14,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,西凤学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.35,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:45.64,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,你看起来很郁闷的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:48.10,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.81,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,没 没什么啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.14,0:01:55.60,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,这样的话 我来给你量量吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:58.02,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,诶!? 我就免了!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:00.47,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,不用跟我客气~来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:04.06,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,我来看看…73公分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:05.60,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,哎呀 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:07.60,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,可爱? 这是讽刺吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:11.97,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,不 贫乳也是可以很迷人的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.35,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,贫乳!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.35,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,这还不如被叫做“可爱”呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.18,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,你这个坏女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:20.06,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,我可以用闪电装甲来让你见识扩大后的胸围!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:24.22,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,比起那个 还是让我继续揉揉吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:28.22,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,那…不… 不必劳驾了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.39,*Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,我相信我可以把这个贫乳变得漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.18,0:02:34.31,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,别再说我贫了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:40.06,*Default,Attia,0,0,0,,胸部…不需要…仅仅…大…还有色泽都会影响…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.06,Default,Chiffon,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fs24}哎呀呀 是这里吗?
